    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your<strong> vegetable stock mix</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[195ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [250ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
