    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the prawns are coated in the spices, add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and <strong>ground almonds</strong> to the pan and cook for a further 2-3 min or until the prawns are cooked through</p><p>Once done, stir in your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and cook for a further 1 min or until it's warmed through – this is your<strong> mild king prawn korma</strong></p>",
